If I include a form like this:
```{% dnd_module 
          path='@HubSpot/form'
          form={ 
            "form_id": "xxx-xxx-xxxx-xxxx" 
            }
        %}   ```
then the `v2.js` file is included as if it was my own script (instead of third-party). Is there a way to mark it as third party or some other version of this setup that allows for that?
